data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, perfectly situated in a highly coveted school district, where educational excellence meets the charm of home. This inviting property goes beyond the ordinary, offering a thoughtfully designed space that includes a partially finished basement, adding an extra dimension of versatility and entertainment.     As you approach the house, you'll be greeted by a huge corner lot with lots of room for the kids to play. Step inside to discover an open and inviting floor plan, featuring a seamlessly integrated living, dining, and kitchen area. The living/family room offers a cozy space for relaxation, complete with large windows that fill the room with natural light and showcase views of the surrounding neighborhood.    The three bedrooms are generously sized and thoughtfully designed to provide a comfortable retreat for every member of the household. The master suite is very nicely sized and boasts a generous walk-in closet. There are also two linen closets as well as a coat closet to provide ample storage space. The additional bedrooms share a well-appointed bathroom, ensuring both convenience and functionality for daily living. Another bonus is one of the bedroom have TWO closets, one generous walk in and another nicely sized wall closet.     Outside, the backyard offers a large space for outdoor activities and gatherings. A spacious area provides the perfect spot for entertaining and has so much room for building the garden oasis of your dreams! Plenty of room for a storage shed, boat, trailer, etc.    Beyond the comfort of the home itself, the property's location within a desirable school district adds an extra layer of appeal. Families will appreciate the proximity to top-rated schools, making the daily commute for students and parents alike a breeze.    In summary, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home not only provides a family-orientated and comfortable living space but also offers the added advantage of being situated in a coveted school district. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own and enjoy the perfect combination of modern living and educational excellence.
